               AFTER ADVANCING WS-SPACING.
           ADD WS-SPACING TO WS-LINES-IN-USE.
           MOVE 2 TO WS-SPACING.
           WRITE ER-EARNINGS-REPORT-OUT FROM COLUMN-HEADINGS-2
           WRITE ER-EARNINGS-REPORT-OUT FROM WS-HEADINGS-3
               AFTER ADVANCING WS-SPACING. 